ities and their villages:","year":-1443},{"id":"recZjWTulIoQJSozW","ref":"Josh.19.8","text":"And all the villages that were round about these cities to Baalathbeer, Ramath of the south. This is the inheritance of the tribe of the children of Simeon according to their families.","year":-1443}]}
